A striking computational fluid dynamic simulation tracking a mechanochemical state-memory transition inside a non-electronic computer block. An incoming air pressure signal profile hitting a 450 Pa threshold is depicted as a series of orderly, high-velocity blue airflow vectors striking a linear piston gate. The force mechanically drives a low-friction white Delrin micro-shuttle valve exactly 1.8mm down a smooth channel track, snapping it securely into an alternate locked parameter orientation. Scientific data visualization overlay, deep contrast, black background, 8k --ar 16:9
